summary: Ravensburg Art Museum by Lederer Ragnarsdóttir Oei. Set in the medieval town of Ravensburg, Germany, the bricks used to...
caption:
roomonfire-good-design:

Ravensburg Art Museum by Lederer Ragnarsdóttir Oei. Set in the medieval town of Ravensburg, Germany, the bricks used to construct this contemporary art museum were salvaged from a demolished 14th-century cloister near the Belgian border. As a result, the building blends in naturally with the cityscape that has developed over centuries.

summary:
escher x nendo | between two worlds
 Popularly known as the NGV, the National Gallery of Victoria in Melbourne presents a...
caption:
archatlas:

escher x nendo | between two worlds

Popularly known as the NGV, the National Gallery of Victoria in Melbourne presents a groundbreaking exhibition that features the work of Dutch artist MC Escher in dialogue with the work of acclaimed Japanese design studio Nendo. Titled escher x nendo | between two worlds, the show will open to the public from December 2nd, 2018 to april 7th, 2019.
